title: Ep 313 | Jase's Wikipedia Page Is a MESS & Phil's Disgusting Habit in the Duck Blind
description:
Jase uses Scripture to answer an age-old question: Which came first, the chicken or the egg? Al finds Jase’s Wikipedia page interesting — especially the inaccuracies. Jase and Phil believe that people only want a small part of Jesus. Phil points out how crazy the first person who tried milk probably was. And Jase talks about Phil’s disgusting habit.
